<template>
  <v-card
    :loading="loading"
    class="mx-auto mt-12 mb-12"
	elevation="24"
	min-height="89%"
	min-width="100%"
	outlined
	app
  >
  <v-row
  v-for="item in items"
  :key="item"
      class="mb-6"
      justify="center"
      no-gutters>
  <v-btn block      
   	  class="ma-2"
      outlined
	        rounded
      color="indigo" v-if="item.link === 'button'">
	  {{item.title}}
  <v-icon>mdi-{{item.icon}}</v-icon>
  </v-btn>
  <v-btn block       
  	  class="ma-2"
      outlined
	        rounded
      color="indigo"
	  :to="item.link" 
	  v-if="item.link !== 'button'">
	 {{item.title}} 
  <v-icon>mdi-{{item.icon}}</v-icon>
  </v-btn>
	
  </v-row>
  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
  export default {
    data: () => ({
      loading: false,
      selection: 1,
	  items: [
		{title:"Изменить анкету", link:"/person", icon:"home"},
		{title:"Мои фотографии", link:"/photo", icon:"home"},
		{title:"Сменить пароль", link:"/changepassword", icon:"home"},
		{title:"Показывать в поиске?", link:"/insearch", icon:"home"},
		{title:"История входов", link:"/iplog", icon:"home"},
		{title:"Настройки", link:"/settings", icon:"home"},
		{title:"Выход на этом устройвстве", link:"button", icon:"home"},
		{title:"Выход на всех устройствах", link:"button", icon:"home"},
		{title:"Удалить анкету", link:"/delete", icon:"home"},			
	]
    }),

    methods: {
      reserve () {
        this.loading = true

        setTimeout(() => (this.loading = false), 2000)
      },
    },
  }
</script>
